reviewText: had to stop a lot to do the exercise. thought the dvd would do a workout you could follow, had to keep turning it on and off and rewind.

This product came on time and was in good condition, however its the worst workout video I've ever seen. Its nothing to work out with at all just shows different positions of using it. I was so dissatisfied I threw it out after I watched it. Total waste of money in my opinion. Just want to add that this is nothing to do with my satisfaction with Amazon at all, just this particular product.
